title: The Cure - 12:13 Dream [Live from MySpace Secret Shows]
description:
The Cure played a MySpace Secret Show on December 13th, 2008 at the Troubadour in West Hollywood, CA. The show was almost 3 hours long and 33 songs long.

On April 21st, 2009, The Cure's MySpace uploaded this show in its entirety minus the in between chatter by Robert. These are those files.
